想出街，好攰，集中唔到，好似經常都有一啲唔開心嘅念頭想法，如果中番幾個呢啲symptom，咁最好搵精神科check check，呢啲叫做PMDD 經前不悅症，如果唔理佢後果好嚴重。<br />\n但係如果無呢啲情緒困擾，咁搵婦科、普通科（唔得就叫佢寫轉介）都應該ok。<br />\n<br />\nTLDR: 睇醫生啦仲係連登問"},{"pid":"a329fd9939472d6c6078fffc9afd1886624416c8","tid":1531212,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316e5d7d8a8a23bf5c43cc4c6f1f26e735875294","tid":1531212,"uid":225103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:35:05.000Z","msg":"有無生理反應？頭痛抽筋個d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"頭暈頭痛 muscle pain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e6c97c0127a53edab266f1e4c06649b3c6bb88","tid":1531212,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e50bf2d21f691b631f96f3d396a931d1c569df6","tid":1531212,"uid":247493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:56:29.000Z","msg":"要注意嘅係有呢啲symptom之外會唔會份人好depress好唔開心，咩都無興趣，唔想出街，好攰，集中唔到，好似經常都有一啲唔開心嘅念頭想法，如果中番幾個呢啲symptom，咁最好搵精神科check check，呢啲叫做PMDD 經前不悅症，如果唔理佢後果好嚴重。<br />\n但係如果無呢啲情緒困擾，咁搵婦科、普通科（唔得就叫佢寫轉介）都應該ok。<br />\n<br />\nTLDR: 睇醫生啦仲係連登問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:04:45.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要係集中唔到同好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係去睇醫生好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dba815e8bbbd564490f67610d8143145950ba11","tid":1531212,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263db804c8280732614389fee586087e78303b0e","tid":1531212,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dba815e8bbbd564490f67610d8143145950ba11","tid":1531212,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019